         <abstract id="aspace_aee75e57eacdca5c8f7d49b1b7fc803c">Correspondence, financial, legal, and other documents of William W. Starr relating to harbor maintenance and improvements in Bridgeport and Norwalk, Connecticut. Included are contracts with the U.S. Army Engineer's Office for work on the harbors, receipts for material and labor, notes on harbor maintenance, clippings, and printed matter.</abstract>
         <origination label="Creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part localtype="agent_person">Starr, William W.</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
